{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>What is Lament?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Lament is a game focused around the 5 Stages of Grief, philosophy, and overcoming the unique challenges that loss brings to those that experience it. While playing the game you will need to find your way through 5 mazes, each larger than the last with an additional obstacle/twist for you to overcome. These obstacles can range from the maze itself, traditional path based obstacles, riddles, or even searching for key items/locations; and the player will need to use their wits and Lantern to see the path ahead..</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Key Features:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Low Poly</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Puzzle Gameplay: Mazes, Riddles, Obstacles, and Key Item progression. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Visualized Grief &amp; Level Degradation</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Professionally Voiced</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Hidden Objectives &amp; Black Light Inspired Mechanics</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841370/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737582346","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841370/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1737582346","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841370/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737582346","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841370/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737582346","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>What is Lament?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Lament is a game focused around the 5 Stages of Grief, philosophy, and overcoming the unique challenges that loss brings to those 